ription and when your next subscription payment will be. If you want to see past payments, click View Billing History. Click Manage next to your current subscription to upgrade and view all the features and details of your subscription.' },\n                    { question: 'Unlimited Storage Accounts', answer: 'The Pic-Time Advanced plan includes unlimited storage, but it\\'s designed for individual photographers\\' business only (see our Terms of Service). We monitor usage to make sure the service is used as intended. If your usage exceeds the fair limits (more than 20GB per gallery and 100 GB of bandwidth per month), additional fees may apply. We offer custom plans for accounts that serve more than one photographer (e.g., agencies or teams). Please fill in our Agency Inquiry Form, and our support team will be in touch.' },\n                    { question: 'Need Help? Here\\'s How to Reach Us', answer: 'The Pic-Time support team works 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. We have agents working around the world, covering all time zones and working through the weekends. First, check out our Help Center. If you don\\'t find what you need contact our support team via the chat widget or email support@pic-time.com. We\\'re here to help whenever you need and on any question.' }\n                ]\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n\n</html>\n"
